            Homes in Heritage Plantation typically range from 2,500 to 5,000+ square feet, featuring open floor plans ideal for modern family life and sophisticated entertaining. You'll find premium finishes throughout - hardwood floors, granite countertops, custom cabinetry, and spa-inspired master suites. Many properties include formal dining rooms, home offices, bonus rooms, and three-car garages that reflect the community's executive character.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
