              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>2,500-5,000+ sq ft</strong> executive floor plans</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" />
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Mature landscaping</strong> and established lots</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
